      <title>韩国加强监管 严厉打击加密货币交易欺诈行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/south-korea-hunts-for-fraudulent-crypto-trading-as-rules-tighten</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国监管机构正在加大对当地加密货币交易所的压力，要求其根除可疑交易，这是本月晚些时候生效的新数字资产法旨在加强投资者保护的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/south-korea-hunts-for-fraudulent-crypto-trading-as-rules-tighten</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 07:16:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大陆汽车业务在华增长，股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/continental-shares-jump-as-auto-unit-sees-growth-in-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大陆汽车集团表示其汽车部门在华业务的强劲增长将有助于抵消欧洲需求低迷的影响，随后该公司股价飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/continental-shares-jump-as-auto-unit-sees-growth-in-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 07:15:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员在大选前加大对英国资产的投资，押注经济稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/traders-boost-uk-assets-before-election-in-wager-on-stability</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着英国选民走向投票站，基金经理和银行策略师都看好英国市场，因为他们预计周四选举后将出现一段时期的政治稳定时期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/traders-boost-uk-assets-before-election-in-wager-on-stability</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中印同意进一步谈判解决边界争端</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/china-india-agree-on-more-talks-to-resolve-border-disputes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国和印度同意举行进一步的外交会谈，以解决长期存在的边界争端，这一争端导致这两个拥有核武器的亚洲邻国之间的关系陷入停滞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/china-india-agree-on-more-talks-to-resolve-border-disputes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 06:49:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士通胀因商品成本下降而意外放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/swiss-inflation-unexpectedly-slows-as-goods-costs-decline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士通胀意外缓解——这让瑞士央行官员放心，他们已连续两次会议下调了借贷成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/swiss-inflation-unexpectedly-slows-as-goods-costs-decline</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利表示，随着选举风险逐渐消退，应购买法国股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/morgan-stanley-says-buy-french-stocks-as-election-risk-to-fade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利策略师表示，投资者应该在周日举行的第二轮提前议会选举之前买入法国股票，因为无论出现哪种最可能的结果，市场都有可能反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/morgan-stanley-says-buy-french-stocks-as-election-risk-to-fade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 06:29:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市因选举而上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/asian-shares-head-for-gains-after-new-s-p-500-peak-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于关键选举成为焦点，且美国经济数据支持美联储降息理由，交易员对美联储降息理由进行了评估，欧洲股市上涨。]]></description>
